s in genotypic frequencies every generation.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The population is not exhibiting random mating between individuals.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The population is becoming extinct because the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase a\"><math alttext=\"lowercase a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> allele is disappearing.</p>"],"answer":2}]